name: bounc(e)rupt
description:
Arcs of colors, they appear to bounce. This flow or gliding is disrupted periodically by an eruption (of multiple colors). While the arcs are as smooth as could reasonably be, the flow of movement is somewhat jagged (and that’s really OK).
